2002-1981 (La. 10/25/02)

John DUNN, et ux. v. Gary TERRY, et al. No. 2002-CC-1981. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re State Farm Mutual Auto. Ins. Co.; — Defendant; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Cad-do, 1st Judicial District Court Div. A, No. 449,624-C; to the Court of Appeal, Second Circuit, No. 36,064-CA.

Denied.

*1157JOHNSON, J., recused. VICTORY, J., would grant the writ. TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ.
